title: Steve Goes to the Dentist, Diddy Wants The Carolina Panthers, What's Your Rapper Name and more

description:
The Steve Harvey Morning Show discusses Steve's Trip To The Dentist, Diddy's interest in owning the Carolina Panthers, the United Airlines' dog death and more. Plus the crew finds out what their rapper name would be.
